Race.SpecificTitle: Council Member -- City of Denham Springs
PW School Board -- 7.18 Mills Renewal - SB - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish School Board of the Parish of Livingston, State of Louisiana, be authorized to continue to levy and collect a special tax of seven and eighteen hundredths (7.18) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish of Livingston (an estimated $3,550,000 is reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, for the purpose of maintaining and operating public schools within the Parish of Livingston, Louisiana?
